				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/C%E1%BA%A3m-ho%C3%A0i/poem-LU5HvF0HF-hc34t1_uah6w">Cảm hoài - 感懷</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ch%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%B4ng-thi%E1%BB%81n-s%C6%B0/author-EGSe3PPePPUaSNFMPBLmNQ">Chân Không thiền sư</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/Chi%E1%BA%BFu-truy-ph%C3%B3-%C4%91%C3%B4-nh%E1%BB%8B-nguy%E1%BB%87t-ch%C3%AD-B%C3%A1-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/poem-B17jGCrxBT8IcOW-BQy84g">Chiếu truy phó đô, nhị nguyệt chí Bá đình thượng - 詔追赴都二月至灞亭上</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%E1%BB%85u-T%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-cFCa0wn9ZwJZJ5nwtlsQmQ">Liễu Tông Nguyên</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/D%C5%A9ng-Kim-%C4%91%C3%ACnh-th%E1%BB%8B-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-du-gi%E1%BA%A3-ch%C6%B0-qu%C3%A2n/poem-07KmIjk124GKdIWWR9NHLA">Dũng Kim đình thị đồng du giả chư quân - 湧金亭示同遊諸君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Hi%E1%BA%BFu-V%E1%BA%A5n/author-lCIs61Hzjl6rqKSiwGq6ow">Nguyên Hiếu Vấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/%C4%90%C3%A0o-hoa/poem-6BeJ9HqTz4joMioNaUvhAg">Đào hoa - 桃花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/%C4%90i%E1%BB%87p-luy%E1%BA%BFn-hoa/poem-mmSPKTtkQW_Q2tD7rmgAJw">Điệp luyến hoa - 蝶戀花</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u/author-kQiioNPMMw9jg3d9jImRlw">Trương Hồng Kiều</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Nh%C3%A0n-t%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%BA/poem-SfJjdY1BShl5c2Q2RpHH7g">Nhàn tình phú - 閑情賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="http